#Web View / Document preview view

###iOS classes: BaseWebVC | BaseWebVC

###[acm/execute/pack](http://schemas.isis-papyrus.com/acm/execute/pack) ([agnostic/action](http://schemas.isis-papyrus.com/agnostic/action)) | viewer
###[acm/execute/pack](http://schemas.isis-papyrus.com/acm/execute/pack) ([agnostic/action/collection](http://schemas.isis-papyrus.com/agnostic/action)) | preview

Currently supports:
text/plain, image/png, text/html, image/tiff, image/jpeg, image/gif, application/pdf.

![](Screenshots/iPhone/AgnosticAction/viewer.png)

